data.description: Super nice 3 bedroom 2 bath brick home with attached 2 car garage in Karmen Estates!! Home was built in 2000 with 1,947 sq. ft. on .4(+/-) acre lot! This home boasts an open floor plan, vaulted ceilings, recessed lighting and beautiful engineered hardwood floors! Kitchen has gorgeous white shaker cabinets, backsplash, stainless appliances, center island and a breakfast area. Separate dining room area great for entertaining! Master suite has a walk-in closet and a nice tiled walk-in shower! Spacious deck out back overlooking the mainly level backyard! Plus the garage has ample amount of storage space! This house is move in ready!!! Call listing agent today to schedule showing, she won't last long!!
